{
  "info": {
    "name": "Find It API",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "description": "API collection for Find It backend.\n\n**Variables:**\n- `baseUrl`: http://localhost:9090/find-it (context path + port)\n- `token`: JWT for protected endpoints. Run **Users > Login**, **Merchants > Merchant login**, or **Customers > Customer login (email + password)**; the **Tests** script saves `response.token` to the collection variable `token` and to the environment variable `token` (if an environment is selected). Use {{token}} in Authorization headers (Bearer {{token}}).\n\n**Auth (unified password):** Change password: PUT /api/auth/password/change (any authenticated user). Forgot password: PUT /api/auth/password/forgot (public); admin approves via Users > Forgot password approval (SYSADMIN).\n\n**Get all users** excludes MERCHANT and SUBMERCHANT; optional filters: status, search (username/email).\n**Get all merchants** supports search (name, email, username) and filters (status, merchantType). **Get my merchant/sub-merchant with outlets:** GET /api/merchants/with-outlets — MERCHANT and SUBMERCHANT only; returns logged-in user's merchant or sub-merchant with all assigned outlets. Add merchant / add sub-merchant responses include outlets (empty for new).\n**Get all outlets** supports search (merchant name, sub-merchant name, outlet name) and filters (status, outletType).\n\n**Outlet opening hours:** List outlets (GET /api/outlets) with currentStatus OPEN/CLOSED; Get schedules (GET /api/outlets/{id}/schedules); Check status (GET /api/outlets/{id}/status) returns is_closed, openTime, closeTime; Create/Update schedule (POST/PUT); Delete schedule (DELETE) soft-deletes (status DELETED).\n\n**Items:** CRUD and search at /api/items. Create (POST), Get by ID (GET /api/items/{id}), Get by outlet (GET /api/items/outlet/{outletId}), Search (GET with query params), Update (PUT), Delete (DELETE).\n\n**Discounts:** CRUD at /api/discounts. Create/Update with itemIds; List returns outletId, outletName, itemIds and items. Optional filters: status, itemId, outletId.\n\n**Payments:** CRUD at /api/payments. Required: outletId, paymentType, amount. List filter: outletId, status (PENDING/APPROVED/REJECTED). **Admin:** PUT /api/admin/payments/{id}/approve — sets payment to APPROVED and, if outlet is PENDING_SUBSCRIPTION, activates outlet and extends subscription.\n\n**Customers:** **Login** (public): POST /api/customers/login — email and password; returns token, userId, email, customerId. **Onboarding** (public): POST /api/customers/onboarding — customer details + optional countryName + username + password; creates Customer and User (role CUSTOMER); then log in via POST /api/customers/login with email and password. **CRUD** (SYSADMIN/ADMIN only): create, get, list, update, delete; response includes countryName. List filter: search, status, membershipType.\n\n**Notifications:** POST /api/notifications/send — save notification and optionally send FCM push (include token); GET /api/notifications/unread/{userId}; GET /api/notifications/user/{userId} — all notifications for user; POST /api/notifications/read/{id}; GET /api/notifications/type/{userId}?type=ADMIN. All require auth (any role)."
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:9090/find-it" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Change password",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"currentPassword\": \"old_password\",\n  \"newPassword\": \"new_password\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/password/change",
            "description": "Unified endpoint for any authenticated user (user, merchant, sub-merchant). User is resolved from JWT. Body: currentPassword, newPassword."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Forgot password (request reset)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"user_to_reset\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/password/forgot",
            "description": "Public. Submit username to request a password reset. Admin approves via Users > Forgot password approval (SYSADMIN). Works for any user type (user, merchant, sub-merchant)."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Users",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"your_username\",\n  \"password\": \"your_password\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users/login",
            "description": "On success (200), Tests script saves response.token to collection variable 'token' and to environment variable 'token' if present.",
            "event": [
              {
                "listen": "test",
                "script": {
                  "exec": [
                    "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                    "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                    "    if (json && json.token) {",
                    "        pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.token);",
                    "        if (typeof pm.environment !== 'undefined' && pm.environment.set) {",
                    "            pm.environment.set('token', json.token);",
                    "        }",
                    "    }",
                    "}"
                  ],
                  "type": "text/javascript"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Registration",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"newuser\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass123\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users/registration",
            "description": "Public. Registers a new user (username, password). Use Login to get token."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Forgot password approval (SYSADMIN)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"newPassword\": \"new_password_after_approval\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users/password/forgot/approval/1"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Admin",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Add user (SYSADMIN)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin_user\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass123\",\n  \"email\": \"admin@example.com\",\n  \"role\": \"ADMIN\",\n  \"status\": \"PENDING\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get all users",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?status=&search=",
            "description": "Excludes MERCHANT and SUBMERCHANT. SYSADMIN or ADMIN."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update user (SYSADMIN)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"updated_username\",\n  \"email\": \"updated@example.com\",\n  \"role\": \"ADMIN\",\n  \"status\": \"ACTIVE\",\n  \"merchantId\": null,\n  \"subMerchantId\": null\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/1"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update user status (SYSADMIN)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"status\": \"ACTIVE\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/1/status",
            "description": "Status: ACTIVE, INACTIVE, PENDING, APPROVED, DELETED."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Approve user (SYSADMIN)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/approval/1"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Reject user (SYSADMIN)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"reason\": \"User documents are not valid\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/reject/1",
            "description": "SYSADMIN only. Sets user status to INACTIVE. Optional JSON body with reason."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get all merchants",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/merchants?search=&status=&merchantType=",
            "description": "SYSADMIN or ADMIN. Returns both main merchants and sub-merchants. Query params: search (matches name, email, or username in both tables), status (e.g. ACTIVE, PENDING), merchantType (e.g. FREE, SILVER, GOLD)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Add merchant (admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"merchantName\": \"Admin Added Merchant\",\n  \"merchantEmail\": \"adminmerchant@example.com\",\n  \"merchantAddress\": \"123 Street\",\n  \"merchantPhoneNumber\": \"0771234567\",\n  \"merchantType\": \"GOLD\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/merchants",
            "description": "Creates merchant. Response includes merchant with outlets list (empty for new merchant)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Approve merchant",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/merchants/approval/1",
            "description": "SYSADMIN or ADMIN. Sets merchant status to ACTIVE and linked user(s) (role MERCHANT) to ACTIVE so the merchant can log in."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Reject merchant",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"reason\": \"Merchant application not approved\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/merchants/reject/1",
            "description": "SYSADMIN or ADMIN. Sets merchant status to INACTIVE and notifies merchant users. Optional JSON body with reason."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update merchant",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"merchantName\": \"Updated Merchant Ltd\",\n  \"merchantEmail\": \"updated@merchant.com\",\n  \"merchantNic\": \"199012345678\",\n  \"merchantProfileImage\": null,\n  \"merchantAddress\": \"123 New Street, Colombo\",\n  \"merchantPhoneNumber\": \"0771234567\",\n  \"merchantType\": \"GOLD\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/merchants/1"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Change merchant status",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"status\": \"ACTIVE\",\n  \"inactiveReason\": \"\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/merchants/1/status"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Add sub-merchant (admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"merchantName\": \"Branch A\",\n  \"merchantEmail\": \"brancha@example.com\",\n  \"merchantAddress\": \"50 Branch Rd\",\n  \"merchantPhoneNumber\": \"0779876543\",\n  \"merchantType\": \"SILVER\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/merchants/1/sub-merchants",
            "description": "Creates sub-merchant under merchant. Response includes sub-merchant with outlets list (empty for new)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Approve sub-merchant (admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/merchants/1/sub-merchants/1/approval",
            "description": "SYSADMIN or ADMIN. Approves sub-merchant under the given merchant and notifies merchant + sub-merchant users."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Reject sub-merchant (admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"reason\": \"Sub-merchant application not approved\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/merchants/1/sub-merchants/1/reject",
            "description": "SYSADMIN or ADMIN. Sets sub-merchant status to INACTIVE and notifies merchant + sub-merchant users. Optional JSON body with reason."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get all outlets",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/outlets?search=&status=&outletType="
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Verify outlet payment",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/outlets/1/verify-payment",
            "description": "Sets outlet to ACTIVE and extends subscription. SYSADMIN or ADMIN."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update outlet status",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"status\": \"ACTIVE\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/outlets/1/status",
            "description": "Status: ACTIVE, PENDING, PENDING_SUBSCRIPTION, EXPIRED_SUBSCRIPTION."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Approve payment",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/payments/1/approve",
            "description": "Admin only. Sets payment to APPROVED. If outlet status is PENDING_SUBSCRIPTION, activates outlet and extends subscription. SYSADMIN or ADMIN."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Merchants",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Merchant login",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"store@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"your_password\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/merchants/login",
            "description": "Use merchant/sub-merchant email as username. On success (200), Tests script saves response.token to collection variable 'token' and to environment variable 'token' if present.",
            "event": [
              {
                "listen": "test",
                "script": {
                  "exec": [
                    "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                    "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                    "    if (json && json.token) {",
                    "        pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.token);",
                    "        if (typeof pm.environment !== 'undefined' && pm.environment.set) {",
                    "            pm.environment.set('token', json.token);",
                    "        }",
                    "    }",
                    "}"
                  ],
                  "type": "text/javascript"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get my merchant/sub-merchant with outlets",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/merchants/with-outlets",
            "description": "MERCHANT and SUBMERCHANT only. Returns the logged-in user's merchant (or sub-merchant) with all assigned outlets. Use token from Merchant login."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Merchant onboarding (main)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"merchantName\": \"My Store Ltd\",\n  \"merchantEmail\": \"store@example.com\",\n  \"merchantNic\": \"199012345678\",\n  \"merchantProfileImage\": null,\n  \"merchantAddress\": \"100 Main Road, Colombo\",\n  \"merchantPhoneNumber\": \"0771234567\",\n  \"merchantType\": \"SILVER\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass123\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/merchants/onboarding",
            "description": "Login uses email as username. No parentMerchantId = main merchant."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Merchant onboarding (sub-merchant)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"merchantName\": \"Branch Store\",\n  \"merchantEmail\": \"branch@example.com\",\n  \"merchantAddress\": \"50 Branch Rd\",\n  \"merchantPhoneNumber\": \"0779876543\",\n  \"merchantType\": \"SILVER\",\n  \"parentMerchantId\": 1,\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass123\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/merchants/onboarding",
            "description": "parentMerchantId = sub-merchant under that merchant. Login with email."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update merchant profile",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"merchantName\": \"My Store Ltd (Updated)\",\n  \"merchantEmail\": \"updated@example.com\",\n  \"merchantNic\": \"199012345678\",\n  \"merchantProfileImage\": null,\n  \"merchantAddress\": \"200 New Street, Colombo\",\n  \"merchantPhoneNumber\": \"0779876543\",\n  \"merchantType\": \"GOLD\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/merchants/profile"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Approve sub-merchant",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/merchants/sub-merchants/1/approve"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Reject sub-merchant",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"reason\": \"Closing this branch\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/merchants/sub-merchants/1/reject",
            "description": "MERCHANT only. Sets sub-merchant status to INACTIVE for the current merchant. Optional JSON body with reason."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update sub-merchant status",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"status\": \"ACTIVE\",\n  \"inactiveReason\": \"\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/merchants/sub-merchants/1/status"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Sub-merchants",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Add sub-merchant",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"merchantId\": 1,\n  \"merchantName\": \"Branch Manager\",\n  \"merchantEmail\": \"branch@example.com\",\n  \"merchantNic\": \"199512345678\",\n  \"merchantProfileImage\": null,\n  \"merchantAddress\": \"50 Branch Road, Kandy\",\n  \"merchantPhoneNumber\": \"0772223344\",\n  \"merchantType\": \"SILVER\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/sub-merchants"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Outlets",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Add outlet",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"merchantId\": 1,\n  \"subMerchantId\": null,\n  \"outletName\": \"Main Branch Store\",\n  \"businessRegistrationNumber\": \"BRN-12345\",\n  \"taxIdentificationNumber\": \"TIN-67890\",\n  \"postalCode\": \"10100\",\n  \"provinceId\": 1,\n  \"districtId\": 1,\n  \"cityId\": 1,\n  \"contactNumber\": \"0771234567\",\n  \"emailAddress\": \"branch@example.com\",\n  \"addressLine1\": \"123 Main Street\",\n  \"addressLine2\": \"Building A, Floor 2\",\n  \"outletType\": \"PHYSICAL_STORE\",\n  \"businessCategory\": \"RESTAURANT\",\n  \"latitude\": 6.9271,\n  \"longitude\": 79.8612,\n  \"bankName\": \"Commercial Bank\",\n  \"bankBranch\": \"Colombo Main\",\n  \"accountNumber\": \"1234567890\",\n  \"accountHolderName\": \"Outlet Name\",\n  \"remarks\": \"Optional notes\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/outlets",
            "description": "MERCHANT, SUBMERCHANT, ADMIN, SYSADMIN. Required: merchantId, outletName. All other fields optional (subMerchantId, provinceId, districtId, cityId, bank, location, etc.)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Approve outlet (merchant user)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/outlets/1/approve",
            "description": "Main merchant only. Sets status to ACTIVE."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Submit payment",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/outlets/1/submit-payment",
            "description": "Outlet owner. Status → PENDING_SUBSCRIPTION. MERCHANT or SUBMERCHANT."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update outlet",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"outletName\": \"Updated Branch Name\",\n  \"contactNumber\": \"0779876543\",\n  \"emailAddress\": \"updated@example.com\",\n  \"addressLine1\": \"456 New Street\",\n  \"outletType\": \"PHYSICAL_STORE\",\n  \"businessCategory\": \"CAFE\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/outlets/1",
            "description": "Owner or ADMIN/SYSADMIN. Does not change merchant, sub-merchant, or status."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List outlets",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/outlets?name=&status=",
